Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • Book

  • public class Book
extends java.lang.Object
    The purpose of this part of the program is to create a book class that has the characteristic of a book such as the name of the author, title, ISBN and price. Also, this class contains many methods such as mutators/accessors, toString and others that allow the user to perform the tasks needed
